          content:
            '<p><strong>Protecting yourself</strong></p><p><a href="https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019/advice-for-public"><strong>Basic Protective Measures Against the New Coronavirus</strong></a> (WHO)</p><p><a href="https://www.canada.ca/en/public-health/services/diseases/2019-novel-coronavirus-infection.html"><strong>Coronavirus Disease (COVID-19): Outbreak Update</strong></a> (Health Canada)</p><p><a href="https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019/advice-for-public/myth-busters"><strong>Myth Busters</strong></a> (WHO)</p><p><a href="https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019/advice-for-public/when-and-how-to-use-masks"><strong>When and How to Use Masks</strong></a> (WHO)</p><p> </p><p><strong>COVID-19 in the workplace</strong></p><p><a href="https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/who-rights-roles-respon-hw-covid-19.pdf?sfvrsn=bcabd401_0"><strong>Advice for Health Workers</strong></a> (WHO)</p><p><a href="https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/getting-workplace-ready-for-covid-19.pdf?sfvrsn=359a81e7_6"><strong>Getting Workplace Ready</strong></a> (WHO)</p><p> </p><p><strong>COVID-19 and travelling</strong></p><p><a href="https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019/travel-advice"><strong>Travel Advice</strong></a> (WHO)</p><p><a href="https://travel.gc.ca/travelling/advisories"><strong>Travel Advice and Advisories</strong></a> (Government of Canada)</p>',
          id: '20783965efd24b2e9108eb1c7829d8ac',
